google.description: The first time that I met the charismatic Zachary Cole, I had no idea that he was a multi-millionaire publishing tycoon. I was working my normal Friday evening shift at Annie’s bar and when he walked into the bar on that warm September evening, it felt like time stood still. My brain struggled to comprehend the effect that he had on me while my body reacted shamelessly to his. It was like nothing I had ever experienced before and the feeling really unnerved me. My heart beat erratically and my skin felt hot. He looked so deliciously scrumptious, the thought crossed my lust-addled brain that he could have fallen straight out of heaven. When he looked at me, I knew he wanted me as much as I wanted him. Only one thing put me off – his wedding ring. But Mr Zachary Cole looked like a man who always got what he wanted. The second time that I met him was four and half years later under very different circumstances. I was to be employed as his housekeeper, working undercover to investigate the disappearance of his wife. Fate had brought us together again. Would he remember me? There was no chance of me ever forgetting him. Beautifully Irresistible is a raunchy thriller with twists and turns, and sizzling sexual chemistry throughout.
google.title: Beautifully Irresistible
